{
  "stem": "8786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't want us to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted-- they wanted us to be wiped out or their slave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were marching everybody toward the west.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you get to the west from Kosice?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what they did, they took us in to Kosice, Kosice, which is today the second largest town in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a beautiful Jewish community many, many years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very close with that town, because I had uncles there and I had family there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took us with the-- with-- with-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Trucks?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--With trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us with trucks into Slovakia, into a town Margarita, Margarita.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Margarita we were taken into train, to a big cattle trains, through whole Slovakia, from the east to the west, up to the Hungarian-Austrian border, which is called-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think it was called-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Well, I-- I wounded up in a town which is called Balf.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was probably the station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What they did, these monsters, that they took two carloads in one little town, two carloads in another little town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had brothers in one and another brother there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't give a-- couldn't care less.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we wounded up in a town which is called Balf, B-A-L-F.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not far from Sopron.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sopron is a big town on the Hungarian-Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a beautiful lake over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's called Ferto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] taken over by Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this town was already full of German-speaking Hungarians which is called Swabs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were pretty, pretty tough with anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were taken into-- every house had in the back a stable where the cows or the horses or-- or plain straw was.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
